        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Lets talk hard numbers:</P><P><a href="http://hackersquest.gomp.ch/html/xp/xpchart.html" target="_New">http://hackersquest.gomp.ch/html/xp/xpchart.html</a></P><P>I'm going to assume that these numbers are correct, though they may be a little dated.</P><P>As an Iksar necro (worst necro choice xp wise), it takes me 31,648,980 xp to go from 51-52. <BR>It takes me 677,750,700 xp to go from 1 to 60.<BR>It takes me 85,390,668 xp to go from 59 to 60, hell level of hell levels.<BR>It takes me 285,439,440 xp to go from 50 to 60.</P><P>So, for comparative purposes, if reaching Dire Charm really is 27 51-52s, then that equals 854,522,460 xp.</P><P>HOLY SHEEEEEEEEIT. That is 1-60 all over again, plus another quarter on top of it.</P><P>Kill me now.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
